CreatedById.description: ID of the User who created this record. CreatedById fields have Defaulted on create and Filter access.

CreatedDate.description: Date and time when this record was created. CreatedDate fields have Defaulted on create and Filter access.

LastModifiedById.description: ID of the User who last updated this record. LastModifiedById fields have Defaulted on create and Filter access.

LastModifiedDate.description: Date and time when a user last modified this record. LastModifiedDate fields have Defaulted on create and Filter access.

LastViewedDate.description: Date the note was last viewed.

FileType.description: Type of file for the note. All notes have a file type of SNOTE.

TextPreview.description: A preview of the noteâ€™s content.

ContentSize.description: Size of the note in bytes.

IsDeleted.description: Indicates whether the record has been moved to the Recycle Bin (true) or not (false).

LatestPublishedVersionId.description: ID of the ContentVersion for the latest published version of the note.

OwnerId.description: ID of the owner of the note.

Content.description: Path to the content body of the note.

IsReadOnly.description: Indicates whether the note is read only.

SharingPrivacy.description: Controls sharing privacy for a file.
